### Question:
It is not allowed to smoke in the work area.

Which of the following assumptions can be made?


1) It is an obligation not to smoke in the work area;

2) It is a prohibition to smoke in the work area;

3) Not smoking in the work area is not allowed;

4) Negation of smoking in the work area is allowed;

5) Neither of the above.

Which one/s are correct?
Please provide your answer in the format of [[1/2/3/4/5]].

### Answer:
